room_title: Escape room "Dreadnaught" by Cracked in Wausau
room_address: 4613, Ste C, Camp Phillips Rd Weston, WI 54476
room_description:
The unthinkable has happened - the stakes could not be higher. As submariners aboard the USS-Dreadnaught, you and your crew must not fail your mission. A saboteur onboard has damaged vital support systems and initiated the launch of three intercontinental ballistic missiles.
In this atomic adventure, you must repair Dreadnaught's support systems, and abort the nuclear launch before time runs out. Nuclear war and the lives of millions rest on your shoulders.
